title: (Wed Full Show) Amy Finally Reveals What Was Inside The Package She Got Over A Year Ago + Is Bobby Getting Canceled? + Who On The Show Moved Back Home After 18?
itunes:title: (Wed Full Show) Amy Finally Reveals What Was Inside The Package She Got Over A Year Ago + Is Bobby Getting Canceled? + Who On The Show Moved Back Home After 18?
description:
Amy finally revealed what was inside the package she got delivered to her house over a year ago! Find out what it is and what she had to do about it. Plus, yesterday we talked about how Bobby might get canceled for something he said. Now the threats are getting so bad he had to make a video to address it all...Then, a story came out recently about a mother charging her kids rent to move back home, so we find out who on the show had to move back in with their parents and were they charged rent?
